      "text": "Un dsihwoja prett Rihteem/ kur Tuksnefi tohp ee-eets pee tahs Uppeś Wrat/ jo winnu Lohpi bij wairojuſchees eekſch Gileadas Semmes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Saula Laikâ karroja tee prett teem Agaritereem/ tee tappe zaur wiẍxo Rohkahm kau-ti/ un ſchee dsihwoja winnu Tel-tis/ wiﬀâ Rihta puſſe prett Gileadn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Gada Behrni dsih-woja teem pretti Bahsana Semi-mê/ lihds Salkai.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Joëls bija par Wirfneeku/ un Sawans tas ohtrs/ bet Ja-enajus un Savats palikke Bah-sanâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winnu Brahti pehz winnu Tehwu Nammeem bija Mikaëls un Mesullams/ un Se-bus/ un Jorajus/ un Jaëkans/ un Sins/ un Ebers/tee feptizi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schee bija Abikätta Behr-ni/ Ura Dehta/ ta Dehta Jarwa/ ta Dehta Gileada/ ta Dehta Mikaëta/ ta Dehta Jesisaja/ ta Dehta Jahda/ ta Dehta Busa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Akus Abdiëta Dehts/ ta Dehta Gunna/ bija par Wirfnee-ku pahr winnu Tehwu Nammu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee dsihwoja Gileadá eekſch Bahsana/ un eekſch win-na peederrigahm Weetahm/ un eekſch wiﬀeem Sarona Preekſch-Pilsſahteem lihds winnu Gal-leem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiﬀi ſchee tappe Rad-du-Rakſtos lihdsinati/ Jotaina ta Rehnina no Juhta Laikâ/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ruhbena Behrnu/ un to Gadditeru un Manaſsus puſſ Zilts/ kas ſirdigi Wihti bija/ un Brukkas un Sohbinu neffe/ un to Stohpu uſwike/ un us Ka-rohu mahziti bija/ to bija tſchetr-defmits un tſchetr tuhkſtoschi/ ſeptimſints un ſeſchdefmits/ kas Karra gabje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee karroja prett teem Agaritereem/ un Jeturs/ un Na-wes/ un Modabs palihdſeja (teem Agaritereem.)\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ſcheem tappe prett winneem palihdſehts/ un tee A-garitert tappe winnu Rohkâ doh-ti/ ar wiﬀu/ kaſ pee teem bija. Jo tee peefauze Deewu eekſch Raufchanas/ un tas likkahs no teem peeluhgtees/ tapehz ka tee us winnu zerreja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee nowedde winnu Echpus/ peezdefmits tuhkſto-fchus Kameetus/ divifmits un peezdefmits tuhkſtoschas Awis/ un diwi tuhkſtoschus Ehsetus/ un ſints tuhkſtoschus Zilwekus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo dauds kritte eewainc-ti/ tapehz ka winnu Raufchana no Deewa bija. Un tee dsihwo-ja winnu Weetâ/ lihds tam Laikam/ kad tee aiswesti ktua.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta puſſ Zilts Manaſ-fus Behrnu dsihwoja tai Semi-mê/ un wairojahs no Bahsana lihds Baäl Ermonam/ un Seni-rai un tam Kalnam Ermonam/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ſchee bija winnu Teh-fffff 2 wa\n"
    }
  ],
